div.bibl: Dziennik Zwiazkowy, Dec. 4, 1911. COMMEMORATION OF THE NOVEMBER INSURRECTION

body.p: Yesterday the eighty-first anniversary of the November Insurrection was commemorated at Mr. Narkiewicz's hall, corner Wolfram Street and Central Park Avenue.
Mr. T. Kozowicz opened the exercises with a few apt words and called upon Mr. F. Krocker and Aniela Moszczynska to act as master of ceremonies and secretary respectively.
[Translator's note: Here follows a very long account of the program.]
